description:
Vegetation map (planes) of Western Scheldt 1982 based on aerial photographs and fieldwork.
                                                                                                                             The individual shapefiles of Appelzak, Ossendrecht, Biezelingse Ham, Hellegatspolder, Hoofdplaat, Kaloot, Paulinapolder, Rammekenshoek and Zuidgors were combined into 1 map layer.
